data.description: This lovely 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom Haciendo Style is found in the The Legends At Cimarron community. The surrounding area, Sharyland, is highly desirable. The home is convenient to HEB, Walmart, Target, Cinemark, Starbucks, and Sharyland ISD. Exterior includes inviting patio and a breezy back porch. The interior includes an impressive entryway, ash wood hardwoods in bedrooms, an open layout, stylish lighting, neutral decor, and notable ceiling styles (including minimalist flat and beamed). The kitchen brims with attractive U-shaped layout. More than simply peaceful, the highly functional main-floor master bedroom includes a walk-in closet, a linen closet, and private bath with step-in shower. Also: Steam Shower. The other three bedrooms, situated above the ground floor for privacy, are unique and ready for your decorative touch. Attached two-car garage. Someone's going to be very happy here . . . let it be you!
